<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated to the Secretary of Transportation to carry out <ref href="/us/usc/t6/s1165">section 1165 of this title</ref>—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idb56c46d8-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d" identifier="/us/usc/t6/s1153/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> $38,000,000 for fiscal year 2008;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idb56c46d9-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d" identifier="/us/usc/t6/s1153/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> $40,000,000 for fiscal year 2009;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idb56c46da-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d" identifier="/us/usc/t6/s1153/3"><num value="3">(3)</num><content> $55,000,000 for fiscal year 2010; and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idb56c46db-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d" identifier="/us/usc/t6/s1153/4"><num value="4">(4)</num><content> $70,000,000 for fiscal year 2011.</content>
</paragraph>
